					<section>
						<h2>Pre-Production</h2>
						<h3>What is the project about?</h3>
						<p>A tool to remind me when movies I'm interested in are released&hellip;</p>
							<span class="fragment">in the cinema,</span>
							<span class="fragment">on DVD,</span>
							<span class="fragment">for rental</span> <span class="fragment">(weekly!)</span>

					</section>
					<section>
						<h2>&ldquo;&hellip;remind me&hellip;&rdquo;</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>The application needs a concept of <strong>me</strong></li>
							<li>There is a regular process that checks stuff and reminds me</li>
						</ul>
						<aside class="notes" data-markdown>
							* User model, extra profile data.
							* Email alerts.
						</aside>
					</section>
					<section>
						<h2>&ldquo;&hellip;movies I'm interested in&hellip;&rdquo;</h2>
						<p>The application needs a concept of <strong>movies</strong>, and a link from me to a movie.</p>
						<aside class="notes" data-markdown>
							* Movie model
							* user/movie link is a wishlist.
							* Social aspect?
						</aside>
					</section>
